    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to analyze the MCU chip which is MEC172x from Microchip"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Features"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MEC172x = Laptop / PC Embedded Controller"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "It sits between the CPU and hardware devices and manages power, keyboard, thermal, and system control tasks ."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Features of MEC172x"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "ARM Cortex-M4F Embedded Processor",
        "96 MHz Internal PLL",
        "Package",
        "Boot ROM Secure Boot Loader",
        "Memory",
        "Peripherals"
      ]
    },
